# WillyBeat Preset v2
version: 2
name:    Sparse Vaporwave Pulse
genres:  Electronic, Vaporwave, Synthwave, Lo-fi, Chill, Dreamy, Nostalgic, Mallsoft, Hazy, Bedroom Pop, 80s, Late Night, Sparse, Mid-tempo, Drum Machine
